  <item><title>Version 1.8.13</title><pubDate>Sun, 21 Jun 2026 17:29:43 +0000</pubDate><description>&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Smoother on long recordings&lt;/strong&gt; — the Live AI assistant updates on a calmer cadence (every 20s by default, adjustable in Settings), and the recording screen no longer redraws the transcript on every audio frame. Noticeably lower CPU.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Speaker labels (diarization) are now off by default&lt;/strong&gt; — they ran a heavy background process. Turn them back on anytime in Settings ▸ Diarization.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Hebrew (right-to-left) fixes&lt;/strong&gt; — the summary, action items, and transcript now align correctly in both the live and saved views, and saved summaries read as clean lines.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;New:&lt;/strong&gt; when a Zoom meeting ends, Mila offers to stop the recording.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;New:&lt;/strong&gt; a &amp;quot;What&amp;#x27;s New&amp;quot; preview before you update.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;</description><sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>14.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion><enclosure url="https://github.com/island-io/mila/releases/download/v1.8.13/Mila-1.8.13.zip" sparkle:version="50" sparkle:shortVersionString="1.8.13" sparkle:edSignature="T//jmbGG0MmpwDsgF+CvexnwCPWo4kgLIMRFXznlIphNP0aarJRxovA6cU+I/pdbzsSo0YsjHyx2UjK8s89HDA==" length="140730316" type="application/octet-stream" /></item><item><title>Version 1.8.12</title><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jun 2026 22:15:12 +0000</pubDate><sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>14.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion><enclosure url="https://github.com/island-io/mila/releases/download/v1.8.12/Mila-1.8.12.zip" sparkle:version="49" sparkle:shortVersionString="1.8.12" sparkle:edSignature="yTzdbrM4jwcYNL9ISUqy8zl5bO5juLguRlbyZcNq50oim0aifvx+M4BsvfSSwcrpfx5UdrWBcXrYJe6KZ817CA==" length="140651346" type="application/octet-stream" /></item><item><title>Version 1.8.11</title><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jun 2026 19:23:20 +0000</pubD